{
  "stem": "7069.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The sky looks really red out there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What-- I wonder what's going on there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There must be a fire somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we didn't hear any sirens or nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so, you know, every once in a while somewhere there's a fire in the big city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we didn't think much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We went to bed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Until the next morning, when I was on my way to work, to my apprenticeship.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When I was-- I had my bicycle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, a street away, I went by.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was-- there were a couple of Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I noticed that all their window glass was broken out on the street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And some of the items were still scattered around on the street from the ransacking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Then I came by, with my bicycle also, by the synagogue in the neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that was burned down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And at the moment, I couldn't figure out what has happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And-- but soon, of-- and I had to carry my bike.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was so much glass on the streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I had to-- I didn't dare to put the-- not to talk about riding, to push anymore with the glass.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So I had to carry my bike for a block or two, or something like that, in order not to cut the tires.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then, of course, it turned out to be that during that night, as-- as Hitler, in the headlines, claimed 'spontaneous reaction by our German population against the dastardly crime committed by-- by the organized Jewry of the world,' and so on, so forth.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They pushed this kind of thing like that out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Propaganda was always a big thing, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
